), Vermont|West Barnet]], [[Monroe, New Hampshire|Monroe, NH]], [[McIndoe Falls, Vermont|McIndoe Falls]], and [[East Ryegate (village), Vermont|East Ryegate]]\n}}\n{{VTint|old\n|location1=Waterford\n|location2=St. Johnsbury\n|mile=128.250\n|old=\n|exit=19\n|road={{Jct|state=VT|I|93|dir1=south|location1=[[Littleton, New Hampshire|Littleton, NH]]}}\n|notes=Northern terminus of I-93\n}}\n{{VTint|old\n|location=St. Johnsbury\n|lspan=3\n|mile=128.890\n|old=\n|exit=20\n|road={{Jct|state=VT|US|5|dir2=east|city1=St. Johnsbury|city2=Passumpsic}}\n}}\n{{VTint|old\n|mile=130.600\n|old=\n|exit=21\n|road={{Jct|state=VT|US|2|city1=St. Johnsbury|city2=Montpelier}}\n|notes=Also serves [[Danville, Vermont|Danville]] and [[Hardwick, Vermont|Hardwick]]\n}}\n{{VTint|old\n|mile=132.550\n|old=\n|exit=22\n|road={{Jct|state=VT|to1=To|US|5|city1=St. Johnsbury}}\n}}\n{{VTint|old\n|location=Lyndon\n|lspan=2\n|mile=137.110\n|old=\n|exit=23\n|road={{Jct|state=VT|US|5|to2=To|VT|114|city1=Lyndonville|city2=East Burke}}\n|notes=Also serves [[Lyndon State College]]\n}}\n{{VTint|old\n|mile=140.178\n|old=\n|exit=24\n|road={{Jct|state=VT|VT|122|to2=to|US|5|VT|114|city1=Sheffield|city2=Burke|city3=Lyndonville}}\n|notes=Also serves [[Caledonia County Airport]]\n}}\n{{VTint|old\n|county=Orleans\n|cspan=7\n|location=Barton\n|mile=155.950\n|old=\n|exit=25\n|road={{Jct|state=VT|VT|16|to2=to|US|5|city1=Barton|city2=Glover}}\n|notes=Also serves [[Hardwick, Vermont|Hardwick]] and [[Crystal Lake (Vermont)|Crystal Lake]]\n}}\n{{VTint|old\n|location1=Barton\n|location2=Orleans\n|location3=Irasburg\n|mile=161.410\n|old=\n|exit=26\n|road={{Jct|state=VT|US|5|VT|58|city1=Orleans|city2=Irasburg}}\n|notes=Also serves [[Lake Willoughby]] and [[Jay, Vermont|Jay]]\n}}\n{{VTint|old\n|location=Derby\n|lspan=5\n|mile=170.060\n|old=\n|exit=27\n|road={{Jct|state=VT|VT|191|to2=To|US|5|VT|105|city1=Newport|areadab1=city}}\n|notes=Also serves [[Lake Memphremagog]]\n}}\n{{VTint|old\n|mile=172.400\n|old=\n|exit=28\n|road={{Jct|state=VT|US|5|VT|105|city1=Newport|areadab1=city|city2=Derby Center}}\n|notes=Also serves [[Seymour Lake (Vermont)|Seymour Lake]] and [[Lake Memphremagog]]\n}}\n{{VTint|old\n|mile=177.269\n|old=\n|exit=29\n|road={{Jct|state=VT|to1=To|US|5|city1=Derby Line}}\n|notes=Last exit in the United States\n}}\n{{jctplace|old\n|mile=177.432\n|mspan=2\n|place=[[Derby Line\u2013Rock Island Border Crossing]]\n|\n}}\n{{VTint|old\n|mile=none\n|old=\n|exit=\n|road={{jct|province=QC|A|55|dir1=north|city1=Sherbrooke}}\n|notes=Continuation into [[Quebec]]\n}}\n{{jctbtm|col=9|keys=concur,hov,incomplete,etc}}\n\n== See also ==\n* {{Portal-inline|Connecticut}}\n* {{Portal-inline|United States}}\n* {{Portal-inline|U.S. Roads}}\n*\n\n== Notes ==\n{{reflist|group=lower-alpha}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Commons category|Interstate 91}}\n{{AttachedKML|display=title,inline}}\n* [http://www.bostonroads.com/roads/I-91_MA/ I-91 historical overview] from bostonroads.com\n\n{{interstates}}\n{{I-91 aux}}\n\n[[Category:Interstate 91| ]]\n[[Category:Interstate Highway System|91]]\n[[Category:Interstate Highways in Connecticut|91]]\n[[Category:Interstate Highways in Massachusetts|91]]\n[[Category:Interstate Highways in Vermont|91]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Hartford, Connecticut]]\n[[Category:Transportation in New Haven, Connecticut]]\n[[Category:Transportation in New Haven County, Connecticut]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Middlesex County, Connecticut]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Hartford County, Connecticut]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Hampden County, Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Hampshire County, Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Franklin County, Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Windham County, Vermont]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Windsor County, Vermont]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Orange County, Vermont]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Caledonia County, Vermont]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Orleans Count